You are working on issue kapow-j2l.4: API application_platforms enum update.

## Task

Update api/internal/search/registry.go (application_platforms field, ~L825-847):
- Remove "Universal College Application" enum option (platform is defunct)
- Add 11 new EnumOption entries:
  {Value: "CBCA", Label: "Common Black College Application"}
  {Value: "QuestBridge", Label: "QuestBridge"}
  {Value: "ApplyTexas", Label: "ApplyTexas"}
  {Value: "ApplySUNY", Label: "Apply SUNY"}
